        <section class="methodology">
            <h2>Methodology & Data Sources</h2>
            <p>This page analyzes 25-30 top AI-related stocks spanning mega-cap tech giants, semiconductor manufacturers, and specialized AI software companies. Data is gathered using the Yahoo Finance API, fetching real-time market data, trailing and forward price-to-earnings (P/E) ratios, revenue growth rates, and profit margins. We focus on quantitative metrics rather than qualitative predictions.</p>
            <p><strong>Note:</strong> This list is not an investment recommendation. Data represents a specific point in time and is embedded statically for performance and reliability. Market conditions change rapidly, especially in the AI sector.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What are the best AI stocks to buy in 2026?</h3>
